Not often do you find the biggest rivals in football united on a common platform.

Supporters of Mohun Bagan, who are mostly residents of West Bengal, unfurled another huge banner that read: â€œWhen we were here, there were no documents.â€ Another read: â€œSaffron Brits beware! We taught India to fight the British. Never forget.â€

